	</font>

28
00:01:51,935 --> 00:01:53,655
<font color=#00ff00>
	Und die Feigen.
	</font>

29
00:01:55,135 --> 00:01:57,095
<font color=#ffffff>
	Das, was du eingekocht hast,
	</font>

30
00:01:57,615 --> 00:01:59,095
<font color=#ffffff>
